{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/seminar/2019-04-27-spring-camp-2019-session2/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Heeye Blog","author":"heeye","siteUrl":"https://heeyeah.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"heeyeah/heeyeah.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"heeyeah"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b90a80f2-211d-55e0-a889-de3cb9fd44a8","excerpt":"Why & How Monitoring Why\n장애를 예방하거나 원인 파악, 조치를 취하기 위해 모니터링을 해야 함\n배포로 인한 상태 확인\n성능 개선\n장기적인 서비스 상태 분석을 위해서 모니터링을 해야 합니당. 어떻게 모니터링을 할까요? 지표가 필요합니다아! 다양한 도구가 있어요. prometheus, scouter, grafana 등등… How\nspring boot를 monitoring할 수 있 것 = Spring Boot Actuator\nSpring Boot…","html":"<h3 id=\"why--how-monitoring\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#why--how-monitoring\" aria-label=\"why  how monitoring permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Why &#x26; How Monitoring</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Why\n장애를 예방하거나 원인 파악, 조치를 취하기 위해 모니터링을 해야 함\n배포로 인한 상태 확인\n성능 개선\n장기적인 서비스 상태 분석을 위해서 모니터링을 해야 합니당.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>어떻게 모니터링을 할까요? 지표가 필요합니다아!</p>\n<p>다양한 도구가 있어요. prometheus, scouter, grafana 등등…</p>\n<ul>\n<li>How\n<strong>spring boot를 monitoring할 수 있 것 = Spring Boot Actuator</strong>\nSpring Boot 애플리케이션을 제어하고 상태를 확인할 수 있는 도구\nspring-boot-starter-actuator를 gradle에 추가하면 됨.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Web Endpoints\n<a href=\"http://domain:port/actucator\">http://domain:port/actucator</a> 로 확인 가능</p>\n<p>JMX Endpoints\nMBeans -> org.springframework.boot.endpoint</p>\n<h4 id=\"metirics-endpoint-중에-하나\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#metirics-endpoint-%EC%A4%91%EC%97%90-%ED%95%98%EB%82%98\" aria-label=\"metirics endpoint 중에 하나 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>metirics (endpoint 중에 하나)</h4>\n<p>JVM Metrics, JDBC Metrics, Web Metrics…</p>\n<h5 id=\"metrics-endpoints\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#metrics-endpoints\" aria-label=\"metrics endpoints permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>metrics Endpoints</h5>\n<p>RED Method\nThree key metrics you should measure - Tom Wilkie\n(Request) Rate 요청의 수\n(Request) Errors 요청의 비중\n(Request) Duration 요청의 응답시간\n클라우드, 서버리스 이런 게 늘어나면서 서버를 모니터링하기보단 서비스를 모니터링하게 되는 게 중요해진듯.</p>\n<h5 id=\"metrics-third-party-library\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#metrics-third-party-library\" aria-label=\"metrics third party library permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>metrics third-party library</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>hystrix?\nCircuit breaker - 장애내성/지연내성</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"micrometer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#micrometer\" aria-label=\"micrometer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Micrometer</h3>\n<p> like slf4j, 추상화된 인터페이스를 제공.</p>\n<h3 id=\"actutator--micrometer-demo\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#actutator--micrometer-demo\" aria-label=\"actutator  micrometer demo permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Actutator &#x26; Micrometer Demo</h3>\n<p> 미터 레이즈스트 리 주입받아서 사용\n프로젝트에 한번  모니터링 라이브러리 넣어서 해봐야 겠음</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[Spring Camp 2019] Monitoring with Actuator","date":"April 27, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/seminar/2019-04-27-spring-camp-2019-session2/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/seminar/2019-04-27-spring-camp-2019-session1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Spring Camp 2019] 실전에 써먹는 스프링 부트","category":"seminar","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/dev/2019-05-12-heap/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[자료구조] 힙과 우선순위큐에 대하여","category":"dev","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","521680639"]}